```

Update the `Root` component's provider tree to wrap `ExtensionProvider` with `EventStreamProvider`:

```typescript
<QueryClientProvider client={queryClient}>
  <TransportProvider transport={transport}>
    <EventStreamProvider>
      <ExtensionProvider deps={extensionDeps}>
        <PasscodeGateWrapper>
